/*
 * Connect-C Comprehensive Test Suite
 *
 * Test Coverage:
 * - Connection creation
 * - Connection closure
 * - Send operations
 * - Receive operations
 * - File descriptor access
 * - Multiple connections
 * - Error handling
 * - Memory safety and lifecycle
